<head><title>Symptoms of a Heart Attack: Knowledge could save your life</title>
<meta name="description" content="Knowing the common symptoms of a heart attack could ensure that treatment is sought in time.">
<meta name="keywords" content="symptoms of a heart attack, cardiac arrest, heart attack, coronary artery, indigestion, nausea, heart problems">
<link href="http://www.medicalonline.com.au/main.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
</head>
